# HOW TO GET YOUR SUPABASE DATABASE PASSWORD:
#   1. Go to https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/roqrkkzaayrzarpdnuvx
#   2. Click Settings → Database
#   3. Scroll to "Connection string" → select "URI" tab
#   4. Copy the full connection string (it includes your password)
